    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the body panels are perfectly straight with no imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine original condition, with the leather still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear. Every feature and electronic component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is spotlessly clean, reflecting a life of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 49000.0,
