    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is clean, showing only minor cosmetic imperfections like small stone chips and light surface scratches typical for its age. Inside, the cabin is well-preserved and free of major wear. Mechanically, the car is sound, providing a reliable and comfortable driving experience for its next owner.",
