    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to be amazed by this absolute showstopper! This car is in pristine, showroom-quality condition, looking and performing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Every detail is flawless, from the sparkling finish to the spotless interior, making it a dream find for any driver who appreciates perfection. Truly a rare gem that's ready for its next proud owner!",
      "price": 49900.0,
